  "detailed_description": "Join Cinnamon on this 3D platforming adventure, and rescue his captive Red Panda family from the evil Wu-Long and his band of Snow Leopards! <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Create your own platforms and attack enemies using your trusty shied, Dun!<br></li><li>Explore unique environments and collect a variety of items!<br></li><li>Free your captive Red Panda friends!<br></li><li>Explore the Gallery mode for an in-depth look inside the game!<br></li><li>Controllers are both supported and recommended.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Join Cinnamon on this 3D platforming adventure, and rescue his captive Red Panda family from the evil Wu-Long and his band of Snow Leopards! <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Create your own platforms and attack enemies using your trusty shied, Dun!<br></li><li>Explore unique environments and collect a variety of items!<br></li><li>Free your captive Red Panda friends!<br></li><li>Explore the Gallery mode for an in-depth look inside the game!<br></li><li>Controllers are both supported and recommended.</li></ul>",
